<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 63. Clubiona spp. of the C. corticalis group, male palp, retrolateral view A C. cochlearis B C. rama C C. subrama D C. zhigangi sp. nov., holotype. Abbreviations: C = conductor; E = embolus; RTA = retrolateral tibial apophysis; VTA = ventral tibial apophysis. Scale bars: 0.2 mm." , "Figure 53. Clubiona spp. of the C. corticalis group, male palp, ventral view A C. cochlearis B C. rama C C. subrama D C. zhigangi sp. nov., holotype. Abbreviations: C = conductor; E = embolus. Scale bars: 0.2 mm." , "Figure 14. Male habitus of Clubiona rama. A dorsal view B ventral view C lateral view. Scale bar: 2 mm (equal for A-C)." , "Figure 13. Male palp of Clubiona rama A prolateral view B retrolateral view C bulb, prolateral view D bulb, ventral view E bulb, retrolateral view. Abbreviations: C = conductor; E = embolus; EB = embolar base; RTA = retrolateral tibial apophysis; VTA = ventral tibial apophysis. Scale bars: 0.2 mm (equal for A, B, equal for C-E)." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/535472" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/535462" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/535423" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/535422" .

